SIMPLE: untraveled
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Untraveled
<hw>Un*trav"eled</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Written also
<ets>untravelled</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Not traveled; not trodden by passengers; <as>as, an
<ex>untraveled</ex> forest</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Having never visited foreign countries; not having
gained knowledge or experience by travel; <as>as, an <ex>untraveled</ex>
Englishman</as>.</def> <rj><au>Addison.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Untread</ent>⟦br⟧
